Bouchard shares goodnight kiss photo with fan Will they go on a second date? Post to Facebook Bouchard shares goodnight kiss photo with fan Will they go on a second date?  //ftw.usatoday.com/2017/02/genie-bouchard-super-bowl-bet-date-nets-bucks-game-goodnight-kiss-photos-videos/   Bouchard shares goodnight kiss photo with fan Charles Curtis , USA TODAY 12:13 p.m. ET Feb. 16, 2017 
Feb 15, 2017; Brooklyn, NY, USA; Canadian professional tennis player Eugenie "Genie" Bouchard (L) and her Super Bowl Twitter bet date John Goehrke (R) arrive at Barclays Center prior to the game   Bucks. Mandatory Credit: Anthony Gruppuso-USA TODAY Sports ORG XMIT: USATSI-325032 ORIG FILE ID: 20170215_ads_ag9_058.JPG (Photo: Anthony Gruppuso-USA TODAY Sports) 
You have to give tennis star Genie Bouchard a ton of credit - she followed through on a Super Bowl bet made with a random dude on Twitter and actually went on a date with him at Wednesday night's Nets-Bucks game. 
Good times appeared to have been had courtside:
